item.description:
Come join us for a FREE Intro to Wicca discussion group on Thursday,
September 9th from 7:00- 9:00 pm
to find out what Wicca really is, and what it is NOT.

Learn about the Wiccan beliefs and misconceptions, and some interesting tidbits that most people don't know!

This discussion group is for beginners who want to learn about
what Wicca is truly about, and also for those more ADVANCED in the craft who would like to join the discussion and learn more about the class content of my upcoming Witchcraft Training series that begins September 29 th.

Each course builds upon another, and upon completion the student will obtain the knowledge and certificate to the Level of the First Degree.

PLEASE PARK next door at The Copper Stallion, and come in Cornerstones front door-

Look forward to a night of questions and discussions, and YUMMY snacks!

Hope to see you there!:)
item.name: Intro to Wicca: Free Discussion
